ing: 6 baking potatoes, cut into 1/4 inch slices
des: "These fries are similar to those you can buy on the street sides out of trailer trucks except these are baked instead of deep fried."
ins:
Preheat oven to 400 degrees F (200 degrees C).
Coat potato slices with vegetable oil.  Sprinkle with seasoned salt.
Bake in preheated oven for 45 minutes, or until golden brown.
